title: Doctor Who - The Moonbase (DVD rip)
description:
The Moonbase is the partly missing sixth serial of the fourth season in the British science fiction television series Doctor Who, which was first broadcast in four weekly parts from 11 February to 4 March 1967. The story features the return, and first redesign, of the Cybermen. It is the fifth now-incomplete Doctor Who serial to be released with full-length animated reconstructions of its two missing episodes.
